Nightshade leather is resistant to slash.  Mid Tank is vulnerable to pierce.  Add the small evade stun from the Hib Pierce line, and they will be doing very well against tanks- both Alb and Mid. <br>
<br>
In summary YES you are the only one who thinks this is silly because assassins was refering to pre patch Infils (not Cross realm assasins) with thrust and D'Fang against MIDGARD HEALERS (not cross realm healers) and Midgard tanks (not cross realm tanks).  <br>
<br>
