Knock, knock.  Anybody home in there?  PRE PATCH infs could kill healers (the class) and tanks because of the 15% BONUS TO CHAIN.  If the tank was slash he had his own 15% bonus vs us.  Now you guys get a 30% bonus to the Hib version of chain.  And lots of classes have abilities or spells that make them a pain in the ass, not just your new targets.  You seem to forget that your poor little defenseless healers have INSTA stun and INSTA mez.  That combined with a whistle makes them a royal pain in the ass unless done right.  Now i'm not talking about any other class balance issues, i'm talking about the resistances and target choices.  Yes there are only 4 classes you get a bonus too now and they're all hib.  Thats compared to the whopping 5 midgard classes i have a choice from 2 of which have insta stun/mez and the others will likely be swinging a hammer at me (30% bonus now).  Yell about them changing your class role, about not getting what your paid for.  But don't say that inf have it so easy against your tanks and healing classes and you have it so hard against the hib tanks and healing classes.<br>
